                <section class="comment-body font-light"><p>Hey Jaroslaw, <br><br>This is one of the reasons why USB microphones are not supported.<br>We recommend using the same device for both input and output because then the same clocking source would be used for both signal streams.<br>Using a USB microphone would require the use of a separate output device and often facilitate timing discrepancies inhibiting proper measurements.<br><br></p></section>
